    <header class="faq-page-header">
        <h1>✦ Volo v1.0.0 — Premiere Release</h1>
        <p class="changelist-intro">
            Welcome to the official premiere of Volo, the premium mechanical split-flap screensaver designed
            exclusively for macOS. This release transforms your desktop into a high-fidelity, tactile display that
            brings the timeless elegance of mechanical signage to your modern workspace.
        </p>
    </header>

    <div class="changelist-content">
        <div class="changelist-section">
            <h2>🎨 Cinema-Grade Mechanical Visuals</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <strong>High-Fidelity Rendering</strong>
                    Experience a detailed 132-slot mechanical grid featuring realistic 3D lighting, depth-mapped shadows, and authentic physical pins.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>"Vesta-Grade" Physics</strong>
                    Every tile flip utilizes a custom decelerating curve that mimics real-world mechanical inertia and weight.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Elegant Themes</strong>
                    Choose between Day (high-contrast), Night (low-light), and Lume (neon glow) to match your environment.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="changelist-section">
            <h2>🎵 Intelligent Content Modes</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <strong>Rhythmic Clock</strong>
                    A beautiful, synchronized time and date display that refreshes with a satisfying mechanical sweep.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Live Weather</strong>
                    Real-time conditions and temperature updates based on your precise location.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Dynamic Music</strong>
                    Automatic track detection for Apple Music and Spotify, displaying your current artist and song title as you listen.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Curated Quotes</strong>
                    A rolling selection of inspirational, short-form quotes optimized for the mechanical aesthetic.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Custom Board</strong>
                    Use the "Custom" mode to display your own personalized messages or reminders.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="changelist-section">
            <h2>🖱️ Seamless macOS Integration</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <strong>Glassmorphic Settings</strong>
                    A modern, translucent settings panel that utilizes native macOS vibrancy to feel like a part of the OS.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Smart Tray Interaction</strong>
                    Left-click instantly opens settings, while right-click provides a clean utility menu for quick preferences.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Global Shortcuts</strong>
                    Start your screensaver instantly with a customizable keyboard command.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Pro-Agent Mode</strong>
                    Run Volo as a lightweight background agent that stays out of your way until you need it.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="changelist-section">
            <h2>🛡️ Performance & Care</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <strong>OLED Health Protection</strong>
                    Built-in "Anti-Burn-In" technology featuring subtle pixel-jitter and intelligent auto-dimming for long-term display safety.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>60fps Optimization</strong>
                    Powered by the Web Animations API for buttery-smooth performance that won't drain your battery.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Apple Notarized</strong>
                    Fully signed and verified by Apple, ensuring a safe, "warning-free" installation and launch experience.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

